data.description: Motivated Seller and will provide a home warranty! RANCH STYLE HOME WITH ROCKING CHAIR FRONT PORCH and 2 car garage and no HOA fees!! Brand New Roof and no HOA!!!! Less than 5 min to I-85; 17 minutes to the Tanger Outlets in Commerce, 18 minutes to Toccoa and approx. 40 min. to Anderson SC and Lake Hartwell. This home features hardwood flooring through home with carpet in the bedrooms and LVT in bathrooms. There are newly custom-built cabinets in the kitchen with granite counter tops with farmhouse sink and faucet. Kitchen also features a large breakfast bar and a walk-in pantry with built in spice rack. Living room has a large open floor plan, great for entertaining family and friends. Large master bedroom with walk in closet and bathroom with double vanity. Don't miss out on this move in ready home!
